author: cbs8
title: Police investigate fatal shooting in Vicksburg
text:
VICKSBURG, Miss. (AP) - Vicksburg police are investigating a shooting that left one man dead.
Multiple news outlets say the shooting happened late Wednesday night.
Police say the victim was taken to a nearby hospital, where he died in the emergency room.
Investigators say a motive for the shooting has not been determined, and no one is in custody.
